                <summary>Governor Walker made a number of appointments for Staunton and Augusta.
                    Staunton Councilmen: W. M. Allen, George Baylor, James W. Crawford, Robert G.
                    Bickle, James H. Waters, J. H. Blackley, A. F. Gilkeson, William B. Kayser,
                    William A. Burke, William J. Nelson, W. S. McChesney, and P. B. Hoge. Justices
                    of the Peace for Augusta: William J. Nelson, Henry Harrison, J. C. Marquis, F.
                    M. Young, B. O. Ferguson, George B. Rusmisel, A. A. McPheeters, William H. Cale,
                    L. Bumgardner, W. T. Rush, William Caldwell, James W. Patrick, James G.
                    Patterson, Thomas S. Hogshead, Jacob Trevv, Philip Airheart, John S. Guy, Samuel
